        "description": "SO ORDERED, re (7 in 1:19-cv-00298-CFC) (14 in 1:18-cv-01669-CFC) Stipulation and Order Regarding Consolidation and Stay of Proceedings filed by Stephen Jurvetson, Tesla, Inc., James Murdoch, Brad Buss, Kimbal Musk, Linda Johnson Rice, Ira Ehrenpreis, Antonia Gracias, Robyn Denholm. The Consolidated Shareholder Derivative Action shall be captioned In re Tesla, Inc.Shareholder Derivative Litigation, Case No. 18-cv-01669-CFC. All documents or pleadings filed in the Consolidated Derivative Action shall include the caption of the consolidated case, be served on all parties within such cases, and be filed only in the lead case, 18-cv-1669-CFC. Case stayed. See stipulation for further details. Signed by Judge Colm F. Connolly on 2/25/2019. Associated Cases: 1:18-cv-01669-CFC, 1:19-cv-00298-CFC(fms) (Entered: 02/25/2019)",
